          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The yield curve of the reaction Rh103(g,p) was",
                " measured for maximum energies lying in the range from",
                " 14.5 TO 32.5 MeV.",
                "The cross section reaches the value 8.0(1.5) mb at the",
                " maximum  at  19.0(0.5) MeV (halfwidth of the peak  is",
                " 5.5 MeV). After a drop in the vicinity of 21 - 23 MeV",
                " an increase of the cross section  is  observed  which",
                " apparently   was   related   to  electric  quadrupole",
                " absorption in the region of 25 - 30 MeV up to 32 MeV.",
                "The  integrated   cross  section  for  the   (gamma,p)",
                " reaction is 85+-15 MeV*mb."
              ]
            }
          ],
